oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Cowan, McClung & Co. Building
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Thompson Brothers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Cowan, McClung & Co. Building, Gay Street, Knoxville, TN. Sign on side of building for Anderson, Dulin, Varnell Company. Cars parked on street at left. At right: Miller's, #506 Askin & Marine Company, Spence Shoe Company (Spence The Florsheim Shoe), and partial view of Riviera Theatre. Traffic tower at far right.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Streets; Business enterprises; Motion picture theaters; traffic towers; Shoe stores; Automobiles;
